{"tid":2038924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【推上熱門，有請小鳳姐】開心還開心 有啲野想講","createTime":"2020-05-27T19:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T03:54:52.000Z","uid":40286,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4928a153b1efb006a52aebd73551cef8ef4b8d0d","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:09:49.000Z","msg":"開心還開心 睇返清個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢個只係開始</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMchfEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMchfEC.jpg&h=ae4095bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以預視嘅係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>嚟緊嘅路會好難行</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推得國安法 <br />\n中共就一定會變本加厲赤化香港<br />\n記得要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>時刻警剔自己唔好比中共同化</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCy4FaR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCy4FaR.png&h=53fad4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港唔只係一個地方 仲係一班人<br />\n一定要<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">保存住本土文化 傳承本土意識落去</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不破不立</span></span></strong> <br />\n要浴火重生就一定要<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勿忘初心</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n對外：組織獨立運動、海外建國 whatever<br />\n<br />\n對內：加大力度宣揚本土文化 民族意識<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊就係Season 2 有排都未大結局 頂住<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一息尚存 等待時機重光香港</strong></span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">民族自強 香港獨立</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Be4GHqW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBe4GHqW.png&h=46228ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c8a72c4805c797ca71a7cdfd4148e097a2e320c","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTkZt6C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTkZt6C.png&h=2c5b82db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab539d39dc08c24149513daae7cb2de03407d19d","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:12:15.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e054424b57c910a1180e41c752a877314c03318b","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"民族自強 香港獨立"},{"pid":"dee8606f5a9eb3e21577636b3839a73a2800f966","tid":2038924,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:13:10.000Z","msg":"Yes agger"},{"pid":"98ef9f61e51eaf0896cea9572588e41b6d082691","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:14:22.000Z","msg":"可以算係階段性勝利<br />\n但唔好過份解讀 有排我地受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 係開心嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e9091ff743715afac760fc44274de76f81dba1","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dee8606f5a9eb3e21577636b3839a73a2800f966","tid":2038924,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:13:10.000Z","msg":"Yes agger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8c2c3118f59eac79a8fa0fc8f55bc2a9790fc3","tid":2038924,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2